有关。 不过，排除了月船三号，有人又提出这可能是 PSLV 火箭的燃料箱。PSLV 是印度航天局用来向太空发射卫星的极地卫星运载火箭。 印度航天局局长 S Somanath 对此表示，这个物体肯定是火箭的一部分，但可能来自印度，也可能不是。印度航天局只有通过分析才能确定。%2Fs74BTMiArv2JLJMnTx%2BrXCXZYSBlG3fCJSX8k43Qj0nJ59Djyf8EMszeSYtDvcV%2F%2BAr6Vwb1zdVLjnLT5je%3D%3D&appver=16.5.1_qqnews_7.1.80&openid=o04IBALBiiZxU3pdpo_ziMrBGa5w&key=&version=18002730&devicetype=iOS15.5&wuid=oDdoCt5gkIu0I_dII4Vv5Zg5rU7k"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c18466b1cfbc62d5bec2ca427a1e2de_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/613228016"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4InJ2S/OvczjkQAxoIOTg1NTMzMzYgvq7npQYwADjVAUAscgk2MTMyMjgwMTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1690085351.558542", "card_id": "Q_603996661", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 237}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "成年人看动漫会让人觉得你还没长大吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-53ded3bcac683f6a94f1074f3cf51ee4_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603996661"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4InJ2S/OvczjkQAxoIOTY1MDE2NDMgu9/aowYwADi2AkAtcgk2MDM5OTY2NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1690085351.558750", "card_id": "Q_613310736", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《奔跑吧》第七季第十二期泰国之旅（收官期）？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d959e7136c9c800f00dc271f7171d3f_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "tren